{"tid":2399571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"筲箕灣官中兩染疫中六生曾回校考試 逾百人需檢疫","createTime":"2021-02-08T08:56:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T09:11:28.000Z","uid":312744,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c3d053d79db0b2e8a980560ffb93c04215ecbc72","tid":2399571,"uid":312744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T08:56:20.000Z","msg":"衞生署衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君公布，本港今日新增32宗確診個案。本港至今累計106宗個案。在確診個案中，4宗為輸入個案，其餘28宗為本地個案。<br />\n<br />\n在28宗新增本地個案中，22宗為有關連個案，另外6宗為源頭不明個案。在有關連個案中，機場第三跑道地盤群組再多1宗個案，檢疫中心送院。<br />\n<br />\n另外，筲箕灣官立中學先後有兩名學生染疫，曾於同一日回校在同一禮堂考試。"},{"pid":"66106ae7701445c8a75ba1355b82990f44a59c7e","tid":2399571,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T08:58:07.000Z","msg":"封東區<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba11aea5db34039c32f623b6ad7613be480693e9","tid":2399571,"uid":1069,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T08:59:44.000Z","msg":"點解三跑仲可以正常開工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要嚟個地盤群組大爆發？"},{"pid":"69cfd0e34e37027d7451b0c74c2faf9967c61a7c","tid":2399571,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T09:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b0fc09e44d1a0d3d57c0379fc022ed32a406f01","tid":2399571,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T09:00:33.000Z","msg":"真擾敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e0098c5abfc90c0a57028a60c9d7ac66b3caa99","tid":2399571,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T09:11:28.000Z","msg":"<img